data.description: Don't miss this darling home in Eagle on a quiet cul-de-sac street.  Spacious lot with room for garden boxes, small boat or ATV/trailer (8x20+).  Lovely backyard with a fire pit, pergola, trex decking, hammock, & drip lines for planters. Many trees including 2 plum trees & shrubs outline the backyard.  2 storage sheds.  The split bedroom design has been well appointed with upgrades and so much natural light throughout. Tile floors upon entry, flowing to the kitchen, dining & laundry. Galley style kitchen with hickory cabinets, quartz counter tops, stone backsplash, gas stove/oven that opens to the great room. Great room has led lighting, picture window, bench seat & vaulted ceilings that extend into the dining. Master bath with jetted tub, natural stone tile counter, tile floors, lots of light and custom walk in closet. New roof, carpet, light fixtures; 10/23.  Garage has extensive lighting. Walk or bike to Guerber Park, downtown Eagle, Optimist Youth Complex.
